{"tid":2252050,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"年輕保安員被控堵路藏武器 辯方指被告案發前十字韌帶受傷難逃跑 質疑警拉錯人","createTime":"2020-10-21T08:19:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T10:40:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"01d71cdb629d9f7e402eab6e1f320595ff635928","tid":2252050,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:19:02.000Z","msg":"去年11.11全港「大三罷」，多處出現堵路示威。22歲保安員被指當日蒙面於港島薄扶林道參與堵路，並攜有剪刀、鎅刀及索帶，事後被控阻街及管有攻擊性武器或非法用途工具罪，案件今於東區裁判法院開審。當日拘捕被告的警員供稱，被告在現場逃跑時曾跨過馬路中間路肩，但辯方指，被告案發前十字韌帶受傷，不可能如警員形容般逃跑，直指警員拉錯人。<br />\n<br />\n張接受辯方盤問時形容，被告遭追截時跑姿正常，並無不便。辯方則指，被告在案發前膝蓋十字韌帶已經受傷，不可能如張所述行動自如地逃跑、甚至跨過路肩，直指張當日拉錯人。張指不清楚被告有否受傷，但否認拉錯人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201021/XJEJL7UQSNCAHKLPUCKBJOU7JA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201021%2FXJEJL7UQSNCAHKLPUCKBJOU7JA%2F&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPQmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=078fe462\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201021%2FXJEJL7UQSNCAHKLPUCKBJOU7JA%2F&h=e28159fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201021/XJEJL7UQSNCAHKLPUCKBJOU7JA/</a>"},{"pid":"5fce76f06153dbcabdf9a77770296c455c8c7377","tid":2252050,"uid":192456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:20:49.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"7d3d7a8a9772680a7d80391f90bbb08b34b45237","tid":2252050,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7679b5225200bb28a24f5d371d50af9478ff1005","tid":2252050,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d3d7a8a9772680a7d80391f90bbb08b34b45237","tid":2252050,"uid":201359,"like":0,"disl